  "technicalDetails": "<p><strong>Features: </strong></p><ul><li> Fully Custom number of soldier</li><li> Real-time movement</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Number of Blueprints</strong>: 3 (character, AI and test images)</p><p><strong>Number of CPP</strong>: 2 (1 .h and 1 .cpp)</p><p><strong>Input:</strong> base &#43; inside blueprint</p><p><strong>Documentation:</strong> In project</p><p><strong>Video of exemple (v1):</strong> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/_BCttLs_R60\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/_BCttLs_R60</a></p><p><strong>Meshs: </strong>3 meshs from the &#34;particle Effects&#34; learn section (warSpoil)</p><ul><li>SM_Cave_WarSpoils_Helmet</li><li>SM_Cave_WarSpoils_Shield</li><li>SM_Cave_WarSpoils_Sword</li></ul>",
